==English==
===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌf|-ʌf]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A blown cylinder of glass which is afterward flattened out to make a sheet.
# {{slang}} [[Pubic hair]], in most cases referring to that which surrounds female genitalia. Sometimes it refers to the actual [[vulva]].
# {{archaic}} A piece of [[fur]] or [[cloth]] for keeping the hands warm
# {{baseball}} {{slang}} an 1800s baseball term meaning an [[error]]

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}
# In American football, to drop or mishandle the ball, especially during a punt or kick-off.
# By extension, to mishandle any situation.

